name: Ras Muhamad & Naptali "Farmerman
description:
Exclusive. Drawn in 2017 to fulfill my undergraduate requirements. This artwork is one of the visualizations of Ras Muhamad's five songs from the album "Salam". This artwork represents the song "Farmerman".

If you collect this there will be a bonus print art size A0 (only for the JABODETABEK area).
